edu.kit.cm.kitcampusguide.presentationlayer.view.converters
Class OutputConverter

java.lang.Object
  edu.kit.cm.kitcampusguide.presentationlayer.view.converters.OutputConverter
All Implemented Interfaces:
Converter
public class OutputConverter
extends Object
implements Converter

Converts a list of MapEvents formatted as a JSON string into the actual MapEvent objects. Only the conversion of a string into a list of map events is supported. Exceptions will be thrown if the string does not encode valid MapEvent objects.
For each MapEvent, the event's data argument is parsed depending on it's type given by the type argument. Until now, only the type Identifiers "String", "Integer" and "MapPosition" are supported.

Stefan
